<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>상품 수정</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/seller-upload.css" />
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

        <main class="container page">
            <section class="page-title-wrap">
                <h2 class="page-title">상품 수정</h2>
                <p class="page-desc">기존 상품 정보를 수정할 수 있습니다.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="seller-upload-box">
                <form id="seller-product-edit-form" class="seller-upload-form" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="product-title">상품명</label>
                        <input type="text" id="product-title" name="title" placeholder="상품명을 입력하세요" />
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>현재 썸네일</label>
                        <div id="current-thumbnail-preview"></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="product-thumbnail">새 상품 썸네일</label>
                        <input type="file" id="product-thumbnail" name="thumbnail" accept="image/*" />
                        <small>새 파일을 업로드하지 않으면 기존 썸네일이 유지됩니다.</small>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="product-price">판매가</label>
                        <input type="number" id="product-price" name="price" placeholder="판매가를 입력하세요" min="0" />
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="product-sale-price">할인가</label>
                        <input type="number" id="product-sale-price" name="salePrice" placeholder="할인가를 입력하세요"
                            min="0" />
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group checkbox-group">
                        <label for="product-is-free">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="product-is-free" name="isFree" />
                            무료 상품
                        </label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>판매 상태</label>
                        <div id="product-active-status">-</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group" id="product-stop-memo-group">
                        <label>슈퍼관리자 판매중지 사유</label>
                        <div id="product-stop-memo">등록된 메모가 없습니다.</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="product-description">설명</label>
                        <textarea id="product-description" name="description" placeholder="상품 설명을 입력하세요"></textarea>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="product-keywords">키워드</label>
                        <input type="text" id="product-keywords" name="keywords" placeholder="예: 비즈니스, 포트폴리오, 템플릿" />
                        <small>쉼표(,)로 구분해서 입력해 주세요.</small>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>현재 판매파일</label>
                        <div id="current-product-file"></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="product-file">새 판매상품 파일</label>
                        <input type="file" id="product-file" name="productFile" />
                        <small>새 파일을 업로드하지 않으면 기존 파일이 유지됩니다.</small>
                    </div>

                    <p class="seller-upload-error" id="seller-product-edit-error"></p>

                    <div class="seller-upload-actions">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">상품 수정 저장</button>
                        <a href="/seller-products-page" class="btn btn-outline">목록으로</a>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </section>
        </main>

        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
            <script src="/js/seller-product-edit.js"></script>
            <script src="/js/common.js"></script>
</body>

</html>